## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of the impact of COVID-19 on technology adoption. The rapidly evolving nature of technology and ongoing changes in work and educational practices may lead to new developments not covered in this report. Additionally, the reliance on online sources may introduce bias based on the availability and accessibility of information.